{SOUTH has an ideal 1NT opening - 
15 points and balanced distribution.

With 12 points, NORTH knows the partnership total is between 27 and 29, enough for game 
but not enough to think about slam. Since NORTH has no 4-card Major suit she bids 3NT.}

